data.description: Custom build w 8x4,8x6 and 2x4 construction. IMMACULATE in and out. Owner says design is 3BR but chose to use 3rd as den. A door and ingenuity could transform the den back to BR. 2- H2O heaters!, 30" doors throughout! 6' and 5' showers! Huge pantry and plenty of storage throughout. Custom lighting on walkways and porch. Large front and rear porch on oversized lot with lots of trees on quiet street. RV pad on side of property for your RV, boat or extra big toys. It would easily accommodate a carport or serve as a garage foundation. Plenty of room on this property for additional parking or structure to meet your needs. Wood fence is recent and nicely done (sturdy). Hot tub covered on rear porch. The tasteful colors and smart layout will capture your attention and invite you to make this your new home! Sold with a one year home-owners warranty for your confidence! 3D Tours and Photos coming soon.
